text: (muḥāmedi hoyi!) beli፡- «yenigisina balebēti yeẖoniki ālahi hoyi! lemitishawi sewi nigišinani tiset’alehi፡፡ kemitishawimi sewi nigišinani tigefifalehi፡፡ yemitishawinimi sewi talik’alehi፡፡ yemitishawinimi sewi tawaridalehi፡፡ melikami negeri hulu be’ijihi (bechilotahi) newi፤ ānite benegeru hulu layi chayi nehina፡፡»
